Rune Changelog
==============


Version 0.3.2
-------------

Released on December 20th 2020

-   Pin `Flask-BS4` version to `~=4.5`


Version 0.3.1
-------------

Released on December 7th 2020

-   Readme Installation Instructions (#6)
-   CLI Auth creates all accounts specified inn `RUNE_ADMINS` and forces pwd change (#5)
-   New menu order (#4)
-   Replace `secondary` with `dark` in buttons for better contrast
-   Add Basis view menu structure and details
-   Add celery_worker.py to rune
-   Extend rune gitignore


Version 0.3.0
-------------

Released on December 4th 2020

-   Check if active_item.parent is defined additonally
-   Add templates and logic to create the config files


